00:15:12.540 --> 00:15:14.760
You know, I had to
scratch around to find her.

00:15:14.760 --> 00:15:19.580
And I did understand that there
would be that punishment scene,

00:15:19.580 --> 00:15:22.000
where, you know, she
cuts the girl's hair off.

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:25.190
And I did understand that it
would be for a sexual sin.

00:15:25.190 --> 00:15:26.960
But other than that
I didn't really know.

00:15:26.960 --> 00:15:29.110
So I had to earn my way to that.

00:15:29.110 --> 00:15:33.410
And then, once I got there, which
was like years later, I realized,

00:15:33.410 --> 00:15:39.540
"Oh, now I have to unravel
for another number of years."

00:15:39.540 --> 00:15:43.190
&gt;&gt; Marie Arana: It sounds
to me that you were,

00:15:43.190 --> 00:15:46.220
almost as you were
learning as you went.

00:15:46.220 --> 00:15:47.520
&gt;&gt; Elizabeth Strout: Yeah.

00:15:47.520 --> 00:15:48.820
&gt;&gt; Marie Arana: Yeah.

00:15:48.820 --> 00:15:50.720
And that you -- and
although, you know,

00:15:50.720 --> 00:15:52.530
