How would you know?

00:20:35.370 --> 00:20:36.670
You know, I assume it did.

00:20:36.670 --> 00:20:37.970
I really don't know.

00:20:37.970 --> 00:20:39.270
Must have.

00:20:39.270 --> 00:20:41.590
But that was, that's, it was
