00:21:04.600 --> 00:21:10.630
But my level of respect for the
reader and need, my need to,

00:21:10.630 --> 00:21:13.690
you know, hold up my end of
the bargain, hasn't changed.

00:21:13.690 --> 00:21:14.990
&gt;&gt; Marie Arana: Mm-hmm.

00:21:14.990 --> 00:21:17.820
&gt;&gt; Elizabeth Strout: So, I think,
you know, that was always there.

00:21:17.820 --> 00:21:19.120
So it's still there.

00:21:19.120 --> 00:21:20.420
&gt;&gt; Marie Arana: Writing
