00:21:53.330 --> 00:21:58.640
But it's a person who
probably needs my book.

00:21:58.640 --> 00:22:03.990
And, but they, but they're
asking for, they're patient,

00:22:03.990 --> 00:22:08.410
but they're not too
patient, and they're willing

