to maybe cut me a couple
of little mistakes.

00:22:12.190 --> 00:22:13.490
But that's it.

00:22:13.490 --> 00:22:17.420
I need to be delivering
to them truthfully.

00:22:17.420 --> 00:22:20.580
And they will receive
it on that level.

00:22:20.580 --> 00:22:22.380
&gt;&gt; Marie Arana: Mm-hmm.

00:22:22.380 --> 00:22:24.860
Tell us about "Anything
is Possible."

00:22:24.860 --> 00:22:26.160
I love that title.

00:22:26.160 --> 00:22:27.800
Number one, where does it come?

00:22:27.800 --> 00:22:33.100
But number two, it is a sort of
