I feel that a little bit
about all of your books.

00:23:00.360 --> 00:23:02.270
But never so much as this book.

00:23:02.270 --> 00:23:04.800
It is, it's a wonderful creation.

00:23:04.800 --> 00:23:10.880
It is sort of a great
view of American humanity.

00:23:10.880 --> 00:23:14.420
Tell us about your
writing of this book.

00:23:14.420 --> 00:23:17.170
&gt;&gt; Elizabeth Strout: Well, I really
started the book at the same time

00:23:17.170 --> 00:23:19.340
that I was writing "My
Name is Lucy Barton."

00:23:19.340 --> 00:23:24.470
Because, when I was listening to,
