00:23:24.470 --> 00:23:26.780
of the mother and the daughter
talking about the people

00:23:26.780 --> 00:23:30.090
from her past, I became
curious about those people.

00:23:30.090 --> 00:23:31.390
And I thought, well, you know,

00:23:31.390 --> 00:23:33.950
what happened to those
pretty Nicely girls?

00:23:33.950 --> 00:23:35.250
&gt;&gt; Marie Arana: Mm-hmm.

00:23:35.250 --> 00:23:36.550
&gt;&gt; Elizabeth Strout: Oh,
well let's think about that.

00:23:36.550 --> 00:23:38.510
And, you know, I would
scribble down some scenes.

00:23:38.510 --> 00:23:41.160
And I would think, what
happened to Mississippi Mary?

00:23:41.160 --> 00:23:43.080
And so I would scribble
down some scenes.

00:23:43.080 --> 00:23:46.570
And then I realized by the
time I was done writing

00:23:46.570 --> 00:23:48.080
"My Name is Lucy Barton,"
I realized, "Oh,

00:23:48.080 --> 00:23:52.090
I'm going to have a
book of these people."

00:23:52.090 --> 00:23:53.390
&gt;&gt; Marie Arana: Mm-hmm.

00:23:53.390 --> 00:23:54.830
